    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "LPiJajK2Z37A"
      },
      "source": [
        "\\W will select all except hole carater"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "awqYiWZGaEB0"
      },
      "source": [
        "\\s well select white space (space,tab,new line) AND  last line is not a new line"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "QxK-8rfNbHOn"
      },
      "source": [
        "\\S not white space"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "2KCNbqDUbZps"
      },
      "source": [
        ". match any character execpet new line"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "dibwTgwLbmTC"
      },
      "source": [
        "\\ ignore any special character"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "-70DlH0Ob4Jg"
      },
      "source": [
        "^ match beginning of the string\n",
        " if we have hellow two or three time add ^ hellow wil select the first one only iy u wright hello simply it willl select all."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "R-nLtqzLcoDw"
      },
      "source": [
        "$ match the end of the string\n",
        "  to get last hellow use hello & - &  should right at the end od test if u have two hello need to select lasr one use hello.$ dot need"
      ]
    },
    {
